text: Steffy Van Den Haute (born 29 November 1993) is a Belgian professional racing cyclist. She rides for the Topsport Vlaanderen-Etixx-Guill d'Or team. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
